 tartup/login\n   6. ☑ Emacs railwaycat\n      1. ☑ Install missing package
 s (only a few)\n3. ☑ Setup eduroam\n4. ☒ Install apps/software to match "o
 ld" device\n   1. ☑ +pdftk+\, use Preview instead\n   2. ☑ Zoom\n   3. ☑ O
 neDrive\n   4. ☐ Inkscape\n   5. ☐ GIMP\n   6. ☐ ApE\n   7. ☐ Fiji\n5. LaT
 eX\n   1. ☐ MacTeX\n6. ☒ Helper apps\n   1. ☒ Rectangle\n   2. ☒ BetterDis
 play: DCC issue via HDMI\n   3. ☐ HazeOver\n   4. ☑ PDF Viewer\n   5. ☐ Sk
 im (PDF)\n   6. ☑ Goodnotes
